    "description": "《失落之城：血色黎明》是一款复古风格的冒险 RPG 游戏，讲述了在一个叫格雷湾的城市所发生的灾难。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965410/extras/f480c49921381127568787867d57ce01.apng?t=1705129108\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965410/extras/f480c49921381127568787867d57ce01.poster.avif?t=1705129108\" class=\"bb_img\" width=50 height=67 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情概要</h2><br>那是一个似乎再寻常不过的午后，大学生丽莎·埃尔默正在一家比萨店为了自己的学费和生计而努力工作。与此同时，在城市另一端的研究设施内，一个秘密实验计划取得了突破性进展，但接下来发生的一切和研究人员们的期望背道而驰…… 在一起原因不明的事故后，新闻记者麦克斯·肖恩奉命前去报道。然而他不知道的是，事故中泄漏的病毒正在将城市中的所有人转化为嗜血而疯狂的活死人……<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965410/extras/e2cb561b8a7595f1612b46b98d5c9fc7.poster.avif?t=1705129108\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965410/extras/e2cb561b8a7595f1612b46b98d5c9fc7.webm?t=1705129108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965410/extras/e2cb561b8a7595f1612b46b98d5c9fc7.mp4?t=1705129108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965410/extras/ac348fc0d301ee33319a73695092eec2.apng?t=1705129108\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965410/extras/ac348fc0d301ee33319a73695092eec2.poster.avif?t=1705129108\" class=\"bb_img\" width=50 height=67 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>精心设计的剧情</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>完全原创的像素风素材</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>由作曲家帕特里克·阿迪加谱写的游戏原声</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在与各种感染者，特殊敌人以及大小 BOSS 的战斗中逃出生天！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>更有多个隐藏要素等待你去探索！</li></ul>